<D>__{truce. we're friends, man.}
<C>__{yuri}
<P>__{(looking to his unopened crates, more and more agitated)}
<D>__{friends?! you can't be fucking friends. last week i spoke to you on the phone. you said you would not rest until every last rebel was dead. you called them vermin. you said would piss in their mouths, you said you would exterminate them like cockroaches. just last week, you said this!}
<C>__{cannibal}
